tafsir[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,225,"Alla Hasbirtaa on Й—en ngoondooje fuutorayЙ—e on; wano wi'ugol: "Wallaahi mi sali", maa "Wallaahi ko non woniri"; kaffaara fawaaki on e Й—um, o leptirtaake kadi Й—um. Kono non Alla Hasbiray on kon ko eЙ“Й“an-Й—on e Й—en ngoondooje. Alla ko Haforoowo junuubi jeyaaЙ“e Makko, MuГұГұiiЙ—o Mo Jogitortaako Й“e lepte."
  2,226,"No woodani Й“en woondooЙ“e renndidataa e suddiiЙ“e mu'un, habbitagol dumunne mo yawtaa lebbi nayi, gila ka Й“e woondiri; Й—um ko "liilaa'u" anndiraa. Si Й“e artii e renndugol rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en caggal nde Й“e huЙ—aade sabbitoo lebbi nayi e ko joli Й—um, pellet Alla Ko Haforanoowo Й“e HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende e kon ko yawtini; sabu O Shar'inirii kaffaara fii soktorgal nden woondoore."
  2,227,"Si Й“e faandorii tertagol renndiigu ngun ceergal, Pellet Alla ko Nanoowo haalaaji maЙ“Й“e sugu Й—in yowitii e ceergal, AnnduЙ—o fiyakuuji e paandale maЙ“Й“e; O YoЙ“oyay Й“e Й—um."
  2,228,"SeeraaЙ“e Й“en habbitaЕӢto ko'e maЙ“Й“e, laaЙ“e tati: Й“e resetaake ndeer majje. DagaЕӢtaako Й“e suuЙ—ugol kon ko Alla Tagi e ndeer reЕӢngaaji maЙ“Й“e; si Й“e laatike goonguЙ“e e gomЙ—inal Alla e Гұalaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en Й“uri haandude ruttugol Й“e ka dumunne edda; si Й“e faandike moЖҙЖҙiЕӢtiЕӢgol kon ko ceergal ngal bonni hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. No woodani rewЙ“e Й“en haqqeeji e wajibiiЙ—i, yeru kon ko woodani moobiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en e Й—um, wano woowiraa non hakkunde yimЙ“e. No woodani worЙ“e Й“en: darja e hoore rewЙ“e Й“en; sabu ndeЕӢka e fiyaaku ceergal. Alla non ko FooluЙ—o mo fooletaake, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e Shari'a Makko."
  2,229,"Ceergal ngal jom galle jogorii seerude rij'a,=ruttaade ko noone Й—iЙ—i:ko nde o seerata o ruttitoo,refti o seera o ruttitoo;Й“aawo Й—in Й—iЙ—i,ko o suЙ“inaaЙ—o hakkunde jogitorgol debbo on no moЖҙЖҙiri,maa seerida mo e unde e huhaqqeeji makko Й—in tataЙ“al;no moЖҙЖҙiri.DagaЕӢtaako moodiЙ“Й“e Й“en,Жҙettitugol seeЙ—a e teЕӢe rewЙ“e Й“en,si wanaa hara on debbo aГұirii moodi mun jikku makko maa tagoodi makko;Й“en resindirЙ“e Й—iЙ—o tamЖҙinora ngun ngaynu,wonde Й“e gasidataa hunnude haqqeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in,yo Й“e rutto ka musidal.Si musidal roЕӢkii,haray goopi woo fawaaki Й“e nde debbo on Й“oorotoo sahrti nde o jonnata zawju coggu ngol Й“ooragol.ЖҠen ko Гұaawooje shari'aaji feГұГұinЙ—i harmi e ko dagii;wata on yawtu-Й—i,kala on yawtuЙ—o keeri Alla Й—in,ko Й“en ngoni tooГұooЙ“e ko'e mun,sabu faandaare halkitagol e tikkere Joomiiko."
  2,230,"Si o seerii debbo on tataЙ“al, on dagitaЕӢtaako mo e desal haa gorko goo resa mo dewgal sellungal, Й“e renndida e maggal. Si on gorko Й—iЙ—mo seerii mo maa o maayi e ngal dewgal, bakkaatu woo fawaaki debbo on nde o artira ka moodi makko arano on desal kesal; si Й“e yananaama (fellitii) ГұiiЙ“nude keeri shari'aaji Allah Й—in. Alla No ЖҒaЕӢnginana Й—in keeri shari'aaji, Й“en yimЙ“e ngannduЙ“e Гұaawooje Makko e keeri Makko; tawde hiЙ“e naftora Й—i."